<item>
            <title>[HBASE-12231] REST gateway authentication should be independent of Hadoop/HBase security configuration.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-12231</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It is reasonable that a user would want to secure the HBase REST interface without having to incur the cost of securing the entire HBase/Hadoop ecosystem.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The current implementation does not allow that and needs to be modified.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
